When setting up a layout and using a LayoutPosition or Gravity that includes Left/Right settings, they are ignored. Eg the following results in controls being at the bottom center of the layout:

```
            UILayout layout = new UILayout()
            {
                LayoutPosition = UI_LAYOUT_POSITION.UI_LAYOUT_POSITION_RIGHT_BOTTOM,
                Rect = viewport.Rect
            };
```

